The paper focuses on improving the performance of TCP in cellular networks, which is a subfield of networked systems and communication. Therefore, cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category. The paper also discusses the challenges of cellular networks, which can be related to security and cryptography (cs.CR), information theory (cs.IT), multimedia (cs.MM), and systems and control (cs.SY). However, these categories are less likely as they are not the main focus of the paper.
